Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.secdns

This defines the classes for the DNSSEC extension.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChgType
    Models the <chg> element as documented in RFC5910.
    DSData
    Models the <dsData> element as documented in RFC5910.
    DSOrKeyType
    Models the <add>, <infData> and <create> elements as documented in RFC5910.
    KeyData
    Models the <keyData> element as documented in RFC5910.
    MaxSigLifeType
    Models the <maxSigLife> element as documented in RFC5910.
    RemType
    Models the <rem> element as documented in RFC5910.
    SecDnsDomainCreateCommandExtension
    Processes the <create> element as documented in RFC5910.
    SecDnsDomainInfoResponseExtension
    Process the <infData> element as documented in RFC5910.
    SecDnsDomainUpdateCommandExtension
    Processes the <update> element as documented in RFC5910.
    SecDNSXMLUtil
    This defines the operations to facilitate adding child elements to a XML Document.
